						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center" id="contact-section">
					<div id="contact-form" class="col-12">
						<h2 class="mb-5">Contact Me</h2>
						<form>
							<div class="p-3 my-3 form-field">
								<label for="contact-email">Email</label>
								<input id="contact-email" class="form-control contact-field" name="contact-email" type="email" placeholder="Please enter a working email address" required/>
							</div>
							<div class="p-3 my-3 form-field">
								<label for="contact-msg">Message</label>
								<textarea id="contact-msg" minlength="50" cols="10" maxlength="3000" class="form-control contact-field" name="contact-msg" placeholder="Feel free to say what's on your mind" required></textarea>
							</div>
							<div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
								<input type="submit" class="py-2 px-5 btn" value="Send" id="contact-submit"/>
							</div>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alerts">
				<p id="not-found" class="msg hidden">
					Sorry, we couldn't fetch weather info for that location, please confirm that you 
					spelled correctly and try again.
				</p>
				<p id="no-connection" class="msg hidden">Sorry, we couldn't establish a connection.
					Please refresh the page or check your internet connection.
				</p>
				<p id="no-location" class="msg hidden">Oops! This page needs access to your location to function properly.</p>
				<p id="progress" class="hidden">Loading... Please wait.</p>
				<button role="button" id="refresh-button" class="hidden">Refresh data</button>
			</div>

			<div class="container-fluid p-0 m-0">
				<footer>
					<div id="smash_credits" class="text-white">
						<p>WatchOut &copy 2020</p>
					</div>
					<div class="social-icons">
						<a href="/connect/?network=github" target="_blank"><img src="/extras/github.png" class="social-icon" alt="DevWonder github profile"></a>
						<a href="/connect/?network=linkedIn" target="_blank"><img src="/extras/linkedin.png" class="social-icon" alt="DevWonder linkedin profile"></a>
						<a href="/connect/?network=whatsapp" target="_blank"><img src="/extras/whatsapp.png" class="social-icon" alt="DevWonder whatsapp profile"></a>
						<a href="/connect/?network=twitter" target="_blank"><img src="/extras/twitter.png" class="social-icon" alt="DevWonder github profile"></a>
					</div>
				</footer>
			</div>
		</div>
